      <div class='post' itemprop='articleBody'>
        <p>In the the 128x64 display, pixels are arranged by horizontal bands of 8 pixels (called pages).<br>The 128x64 object I have written calculates each band according to the incoming strings or scope, thus i avoided the use of a complete buffer (sram2 is quite precious). That's why it can be tricky to modify it.</p>
      </div>
